{"tid":1222567,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朱經緯入獄3月刑期被駁回　即時被押走","createTime":"2019-06-14T12:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T14:14:56.000Z","uid":131157,"like":95,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"71ec3b908619c82dcab1cc6da92651ea4d963cd8","tid":1222567,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:58:22.000Z","msg":"退休警司朱經緯2014年在旺角執勤時，用警棍揮擊一名男途人，經審訊被裁定襲擊罪成，被判囚3個月，朱不服定罪及判刑，早前提出上訴，案件今午（14日）四時於高等法院裁決，法官裁定朱定罪及判刑均被駁回，朱即時被押走，須獄中過中秋。法官由開庭至宣判只有20秒，朱便隨即由庭警押入囚室，朱保持一貫樸克面容，沒有流露任何神色。<br />\n<br />\n58歲的朱經緯，被控於2014年11月26日晚，在旺角彌敦道上海商業銀行外襲擊男子鄭仲恒。<br />\n<br />\n朱的前妻也有到庭，他在散庭後即羈留室位置，相信會入內與朱見面，記者多番追問如和看待判決、會否上訴等問題，其前妻均未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n官：法律不容許過份使用武力<br />\n<br />\n法官黃崇厚在判詞強調，法律不容許過分使用武力，否則，向一個只威脅揮拳的人開槍也會變得合理。法官又指朱當時的想法是鄭有侵略性、沒遵從警方命令。原審裁判官表示知道朱是高級警務人員，以及其在困難時刻擔當的角色和職務。然而，原審根據證據，特別是錄影片段，裁斷鄭沒有侵略性，亦有遵從警方命令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/234892/%E6%9C%B1%E7%B6%93%E7%B7%AF%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4-%E6%B1%82%E6%8E%A8%E7%BF%BB%E5%AE%9A%E7%BD%AA%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%843%E6%9C%88%E5%88%91%E6%9C%9F%E8%A2%AB%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E-%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E8%A2%AB%E6%8A%BC%E8%B5%B0?fbclid=IwAR1XuZOEH8mcbdCtHFM5WkkWXcjEih4BZHsOAmNMt8pSFFwtNogdrW6p1n0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F234892%2F%25E6%259C%25B1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%25B7%25AF%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%258E%25A8%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E5%25AE%259A%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%258D%25843%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%259C%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%25A7%2581%25E5%259B%259E-%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258A%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B0%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1XuZOEH8mcbdCtHFM5WkkWXcjEih4BZHsOAmNMt8pSFFwtNogdrW6p1n0&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjaGgm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=f3376153\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/234892/%E6%9C%B1%E7%B6%93%E7%B7%AF%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4-%E6%B1%82%E6%8E%A8%E7%BF%BB%E5%AE%9A%E7%BD%AA%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%843%E6%9C%88%E5%88%91%E6%9C%9F%E8%A2%AB%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E-%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E8%A2%AB%E6%8A%BC%E8%B5%B0?fbclid=IwAR1XuZOEH8mcbdCtHFM5WkkWXcjEih4BZHsOAmNMt8pSFFwtNogdrW6p1n0</a><br />\n<br />\n朱並非真誠相信鄭仲恒對同袍具侵略性，而即使朱真的如此認為，也沒有理據如片段中從後用警棍打人。法庭認為呈堂片段雖短，但法官稱，須以合理性來決定是否接納被告人聲稱的想法或信念，並同意原審官認為朱的想法不合理。"},{"pid":"4c6c5080cc35b40a294fe07fba7e30dbdedb0263","tid":1222567,"uid":20285,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:59:19.000Z","msg":"逐個清算！"},{"pid":"dd08879077e44c694a85f926c2f83a967d5e9c42","tid":1222567,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c6c5080cc35b40a294fe07fba7e30dbdedb0263","tid":1222567,"uid":20285,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:59:19.000Z","msg":"逐個清算！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:00:13.000Z","msg":"黑警們應當悔改"},{"pid":"3c3ba51abb83fac4f7d868af11d2f59decb44815","tid":1222567,"uid":56453,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:00:43.000Z","msg":"林鄭對朱蛇見死不救<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪受美國佬指示，係都要鋤死朱蛇？"},{"pid":"5fafec8c0ab5e6e490fcebf166906271bf2a022a","tid":1222567,"uid":173179,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:01:10.000Z","msg":"20秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943218d53afacf55f7a91329e0d9c213d7a431a3","tid":1222567,"uid":5939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:01:29.000Z","msg":"禁都係得3個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32feb219d2a5b0ba0cb0ce2dea63ee77281fcd21","tid":1222567,"uid":251925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:03:09.000Z","msg":"手臂延伸<br />\n人唔笑狗都吠 死警犬<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PVxiYCh.gi